said on the phone call.

799
00:36:19.680 --> 00:36:22.456
Rachel went to get a
pen from her handbag.

800
00:36:22.480 --> 00:36:25.376
only she picked up the wrong one

801
00:36:25.400 --> 00:36:30.880
