put this in a text. I've got to go.

855
00:39:03.120 --> 00:39:04.816
Yeah. Yeah.

856
00:39:04.840 --> 00:39:06.000
Yeah.

857
00:39:13.520 --> 00:39:16.176
Well. I was going to
suggest a celebratory bourbon

858
00:39:16.200 --> 00:39:17.800
