873
00:40:21.200 --> 00:40:23.096
what with you not being here.

874
00:40:23.120 --> 00:40:25.640
Well. this is the start of a new chapter.

875
00:40:27.360 --> 00:40:30.496
I was thinking. I could sneak
a few jazz fags into the Van

876
