No. no!

917
00:42:45.240 --> 00:42:47.656
No. Actually. I've been celebrating.

918
00:42:47.680 --> 00:42:50.176
Yeah. I just got off the
phone with my agent

919
00:42:50.200 --> 00:42:52.040
